SUMMARY:Spring Symposium:  Radiant Health
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**Event Description**\nJ
 oin us in exploring the connection between consciousness\, spiritual aware
 ness\, and radiant health. We will discover how meditation\, emotional coh
 erence\, breath\, and inner awareness can influence well-being at the cell
 ular\, psychological\, and spiritual levels. From the relationship between
  consciousness and DNA\, to the sacred power of the breath\, the physiolog
 y of joy\, and the Rosicrucian practice of distance healing\, each session
  blends science\, mystical wisdom\, and practical techniques. During the p
 rogram we will learn to cultivate harmony within oneself while extending h
 ealing and lovingkindness throughout the world.\n\nHere is the schedule:\n
 **10:00 am PDT**\n**DNA and Radiant Health with Grand Master Julie Scott**
 \nIn this experiential presentation\, we will explore the powerful connect
 ion between consciousness\, emotion\, and our molecular blueprint - DNA. B
 lending science with personal insight\, we will examine how meditation\, b
 rain waves\, and emotional coherence may influence gene expression and cel
 lular health. We will also learn how DNA functions as the body’s biochem
 ical instruction system and how inner states can affect overall well-being
 . The session culminates in a guided meditation designed to cultivate love
  and coherence while consciously attuning to the vibratory intelligence wi
 thin every cell.\n\n**10:30 am PDT**\n**The Breath of Life – Elemental H
 ealing with Deborah Nelson**\nFrom the beginning of time\, humanity has re
 flected on the mystery of life. Sacred wisdom tells us that Divinity forme
 d humanity from the dust of the earth and breathed into our nostrils the b
 reath of life\, and humans became living beings. This presentation explore
 s the sacred nature of the Breath of Life\, the intermediary through which
  the Universal Soul interacts with the body. Beyond oxygen\, each breath c
 arries a cosmic essence\, an organizing intelligence across cultures known
  as Ka\, Prana\, Qi\, or Ruach. Whether we are aware of it or not\, imbala
 nce within our psychic body gives rise to diseases. Through conscious awar
 eness of our divine breath\, we quiet mental clutter\, deepen inner stilln
 ess\, and reconnect with our spiritual origin. The Breath of Life is a pat
 hway to radiant health - revitalizing our cells and restoring harmony to m
 ind and body.\n\n**11:00 am PDT**\n**Wellness and Wellbeing: The Physiolog
 y of Joy and Inner Awareness with RoseMarie Toussaint\, MD**\nIn this pres
 entation\, we will explore the physiology of joy and the body’s remarkab
 le capacity to experience inner harmony. Drawing from neuroscience and con
 templative traditions\, we will examine how the brain’s “joy chemistry
 ”—including serotonin\, dopamine\, and oxytocin—supports emotional b
 alance\, resilience\, and connection. Through interoception and introspect
 ion\, the natural faculties that allow us to perceive and reflect upon sig
 nals arising within the body\, participants will discover how inner awaren
 ess reveals subtle rhythms and vibratory movements of life energy traditio
 nally described as prana. The gentle vibrations produced by sacred vowel s
 ounds can also be perceived internally\, inviting deeper sensitivity to th
 ese subtle currents of vitality. Through attentive awareness of these inne
 r movements\, qualities such as calm\, compassion\, clarity\, and inner ba
 lance naturally emerge. The presentation concludes with a brief experienti
 al practice cultivating coherence as well as radiant wellness and well-bei
 ng.\n\n**11:30 am PDT**\n**Giving Spiritual Aid: The Rosicrucian Art of Di
 stance Healing with Ingrid Young**\nWe live in a vibratory universe\, and 
 Rosicrucian students are invited to learn a specific method whereby they c
 an serve humanity anonymously through distance healing. During the 1930s\,
  Harvey Spencer Lewis introduced a special technique that he called "Absen
 t Healing." In this short presentation\, you will learn not only the techn
 ique but also have access to important reminders and best practices as wel
 l as discover broader applications for its use. This presentation includes
  a meditation that invites you to participate at a high level of Cosmic at
 tunement as we project radiant health to all living beings.\n\n**Please RS
 VP to access log-in link. Click Attend Online button below.**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/amorc-santa-rosa-pronaos/events/31374
 4162/
